title: THE Steve Wilkos Show 06.19.08
description:
I AM NOT A MOLESTER:
    --------------------
    A call for justice! Felicia discovered every mother&#039;s worst nightmare when her 2-year-old daughter told her she had been molested and showed marks of abuse. Felicia suspects the girl&#039;s father, ex-boyfriend Casey, and wants answers. Casey however tells a different story, and actually believes the abuser to be Felicia&#039;s current husband, Will! Steve wants justice, and he&#039;s getting the answers no one could. But the truth will shock even him...
